metadata.name: 01 RAYAN - SIXTEENSKULLS
metadata.description:
Channeling the positive energy around #nftparis and my recent skeleton research I have made some imaginary skull studies of the speakers PFP's.  [Updates at SixteenSkulls.com](https://garymcginty.com/sixteenskulls)  [Updates at @garymcginty](https://twitter.com/garymcginty) 


**Inspired by the PFP of @rayan_oncyber** founder + ceo  @oncyber. The world-building engine for web3. @rayan_oncyber will advance how we experience 3D online. Drops low poly, beautifully rendered microphone.



- **Current work process** = Skeleton Studies + Distraction Events.

- **Distraction Event** - NFTParis 2023 - located 512 miles away (16x16x2)

- **Effect on current work** - High speed skull portraits of the main speakers PFP’s

- **Energy of the Event** - Very high ≥9 - Duration - 48 hours

- **Output** = Violent graphite marks contained inside area of 1600mm2
 
- **Read** - “Do not go gentle into that good night” by Dylan Thomas - repeat x 4
 
- **Listen** - The National + Interstellar OST + Mozart’s
